  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4867736">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4867736/" class="title-link">经学教科书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4867736"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jacky_chan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46828110-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jacky_chan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">陳多材</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-03-20"
      class="main-meta">2011-03-20 22:02:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4867736_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  给还行不是因为原书。原书是一本很好的教材，其实写教材就要这样，没有一句赘言。又读了一遍，能体会为什么黄侃当年要磕头拜师了，虽然刘氏人品可商，虽然黄侃桀骜不驯，虽然黄侃只比刘师培小2岁。  陈注的确不行，难怪网上有人批评了。我觉得其实就是模仿周予同注《经学历史》...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
